party/

Owns: Party-wide state:

Roster (add/remove/order)

Shared resources (gold, crafting mats)

Party flags (difficulty, reputation slices if you choose)
Exposes:

Get/update roster

Adjust/query shared resources

Party-level checks (average level, roles present)
Depends on: core, character, data (optional for defaults).
Must not depend on: ui, town, combat.
Why: Centralizes shared economy and roster management.